data.description: What a find! Spaciousness, Beauty, & Location - all rolled into one beautiful home! High ceilings & a grand foyer greet you at the door, opening up to a large & bright dining room and Great room. An ideal floor plan where all bedrooms are divided into three separate areas so each family member can have their own private retreat. And speaking of retreats - the Primary bath is gorgeously updated! You'll enjoy hosting outdoors on your large patio, & there is a large loft upstairs that would make a great office or rec room. With a fantastic neighborhood elementary school, and beautiful amenities, you'll find you rarely want to leave Bartram Springs! With the lap pool, slide, play pool, fitness center, playground, soccer fields, & more, you'll feel as though you're at a resort! Come See today!
